        SayNode(character: null, dialogue: "宿新的速度很快，不管发生什么都像是过眼云烟，尤其是对于他人的事——我很忙，最好不要让我也卷入麻烦——这好像是人们的共识。", dialogueTag: "fuzu", tailCharacter: null, tailPose: null, tailExpression: null, tailAnimation: null, tailRepeatCount: null, sourceFile: null, sourceLine: 19, pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
