        SayNode(character: null, dialogue: "想着这样的事，突然意识到，在研究室进行汇报，到书店，然后是中古店，甚至是逃生，这些竟然全都是今天一天之内的事。", dialogueTag: "fuzu", tailCharacter: null, tailPose: null, tailExpression: null, tailAnimation: null, tailRepeatCount: null, sourceFile: null, sourceLine: 23, pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
