        SayNode(character: null, dialogue: "其一，不仅书的钱大多都被她付走了。就连看电影的钱也是她付的……可恶，当时注意力完全在其他事情上了。不行啊我这样！总有一天我要改掉“只能专注一件事”的怀毛病！真是拜了自己是笨蛋所赐，欠了她好多……", dialogueTag: "angry", tailCharacter: null, tailPose: null, tailExpression: null, tailAnimation: null, tailRepeatCount: null, sourceFile: null, sourceLine: 72, pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
