        SayNode(character: null, dialogue: "-那是你自己的喜好吧！-不对，除了是喜好应该也有一些其他的共通点。-为什么是我的喜好呢……-为什么呢……", dialogueTag: "fuzu", tailCharacter: null, tailPose: null, tailExpression: null, tailAnimation: null, tailRepeatCount: null, sourceFile: null, sourceLine: 25, pose: null, expression: null, position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
