        SayNode(character: "aru3", dialogue: "「接着刚才的话题，在漫画作品中获得了命名的“毒电波”，继而在漫画作品中获得了“电波系”的类别命名。」", dialogueTag: null, tailCharacter: null, tailPose: null, tailExpression: null, tailAnimation: null, tailRepeatCount: null, sourceFile: null, sourceLine: 142, pose: null, expression: "sweat", position: null, animation: null, repeatCount: null, startExpression: null, switchDelay: null, endExpression: null),
